txt.en: Greb once led a force from Fil Gashan, but his command proved short-lived....
Talug was the fanatical general beneath Mazog in the struggle of the Orcs of Moria to maintain their independence.
Defeat the leaders of the invasion within Fil Gashan
Vrarz was once the cook of the Orcs at Fil Gashan...now he shall feed the gredbyg and kergrim.
